```gitignore
## Ignore Visual Studio temporary files
.vs/
.vscode/

## Build results
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
x64/
x86/
build/
bin/
obj/
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/

## User-specific files
*.user
*.rsuser
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## Rider
.idea/

## JetBrains Rider
*.sln.iml

## Visual Studio Code
.history/

## NuGet
*.nupkg
packages/
!**/packages/build/
*.snupkg

## .NET Core
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/

## ASP.NET Scaffolding
ScaffoldingReadMe.txt

## Entity Framework
*.mdf
*.ldf

## Logs
*.log
logs/

## Publish output
publish/
wwwroot/dist/
wwwroot/lib/

## Temporary files
tmp/
temp/

## OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

## Secrets
appsettings.Development.json
appsettings.Local.json
secrets.json

## Azure
PublishProfiles/
*.Publish.xml

## Test Results
TestResults/
coverage/
*.coverage
*.coveragexml

## npm / node (اگر فرانت داخل پروژه داری)
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

## Docker
docker-compose.override.yml

## Generated files
Generated/
```
